OL,7,FOperations Director at Brady &
OL,8,FGallagher, Martin Burns, said they've
OL,9,Fhad to lay off four apprentices this
OL,10,Fyear, adding: "We couldn't really
OL,11,Fsustain to pay them the minimum wage;
OL,12,Fit's quite sad we had to do this.
OL,14,F"We need apprentices, we need
OL,15,Ftrainees, we need them to grow to make
OL,16,Fthe local construction industry work."
