OL,7,FApprentice Aaron Penttila is grateful
OL,8,Fto still have a job, saying: "I'm in
OL,9,Felectrical at the moment but it will
OL,10,Fbring me more opportunities when I'm
OL,11,Fqualified.
OL,13,F"I've learnt a lot with the people
OL,14,Fthat I'm working with at the moment,
OL,15,Fthey're teaching me the best. They're
OL,16,Ftop tier".
OL,18,FBut 19-year-old, Harvey Hall was let
OL,19,Fgo at the start of his second year of
OL,20,Ftraining and says it's difficult to
OL,21,Ffind someone who can take him on.
