OL,7,FIn terms of wages, Harvey says
OL,8,Fsomething is better than nothing,
OL,9,Fexplaining: "It wasn't the best, but
OL,10,Fif you just thought it's only for a
OL,11,Ffew years until you're qualified, now
OL,12,Fit's almost double so nowhere wants to
OL,13,Fpay it."
OL,15,FJersey Construction Council Chair,
OL,16,FColin Russell says this is an industry-
OL,17,Fwide problem.
