OL,7,FHe says: "It's a terrible shame
OL,8,Fbecause we need our young people to
OL,9,Fcome in and be our young professionals
OL,10,Ffor the future.
OL,12,F"They're the lifeblood, without them
OL,13,Fthe industry starts to falter (and)
OL,14,Ffall down and then we're left with the
OL,15,Fsituation where you can only start to
OL,16,Fimport labour."
